Package ca.ualberta.cs.xpertsapp.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Category
    Category class that stores name of a category a string.
    CategoryList
    A singleton to store the list of categories for the app.
    Constants
    A class with only static methods which are used to retrieve constant strings
    ImageManager
    Manages the downloading of images from the server
    IOManager
    Manages loading and saving data from disk and the network Limitation: does not delete local stuff when the server deletes it
    Service
    Represents a Service.
    ServiceManager
    Manages services
    Trade
    Represents a Trade of services between two Users.
    TradeManager
    Manages loaded trades to prevent circular loading
    TradeStateAccepted
    Represents the Accepted state of a trade
    TradeStateCancelled
    Represents the Cancelled state of a trade
    TradeStateComplete
    Represents the Complete state of a trade
    TradeStateDeclined
    Represents the Declined state of a trade
    TradeStatePending
    Represents the Pending state of a trade
    User
    This class is used to internally represent a real life user of this digital application for android.
    UserManager
    Manages the loaded users to allow circular references without getting stuck in a loading loop
